{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/assigning-the-value-of-one-variable-to-another","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Dodeljivanje Vrednosti Jedne Promenljive Drugoj","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Nakon sto dodelite vrednost promenljivoj koristeci <dfn>operator dodele</dfn>, mozete dodeliti vrednost te promenljive drugoj promenljivoj istim <dfn>operatorom dodele</dfn>.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">var myVar;\nmyVar = 5;\nvar myNum;\nmyNum = myVar;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Gore se deklarise promenljiva <code>myVar</code> bez vrednosti, zatim joj se dodeljuje <code>5</code>. Sledece, promenljiva <code>myNum</code> se deklarise bez vrednosti. Potom se sadrzaj promenljive <code>myVar</code> (sto je <code>5</code>) dodeljuje promenljivoj <code>myNum</code>. Sada i <code>myNum</code> ima vrednost <code>5</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5ee127a03c3b35dd45426493","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dodelite sadrzaj promenljive <code>a</code> promenljivoj <code>b</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":418265,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/assigning-the-value-of-one-variable-to-another"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Setup\nvar a;\na = 7;\nvar b;\n\n// Only change code below this line","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Ne treba da menjate kod iznad navedene napomene.</p>","testString":"assert(/var a;/.test(__helpers.removeJSComme